mt: What are the expected effects if the metaverse and the AI are combined?
ref: What effects can we expect if the metaverse and AI are combined?

src: 슬랙에서 아이데이션을 진행할 때 유용한 기능들을 추천해 줄 수 있어?
mt: Could you recommend some useful functions when proceeding with the foundation in slack?
ref: Could you recommend some useful functions for ideation sessions in Slack?

src: 에이아이야, 스타벅스 프리퀀시 열개 모으면 뭐 주는지 알아?
mt: Ah, do you know what to give if I collect ten Starbucks sequences?
ref: Hey AI, do you know what you get if you collect ten Starbucks frequencies?

src: 뉴욕에 있는 존 에프 케네디 국제공항에 가는 최단 루트를 알려줘.
mt: Let me know the shortest route to John F Kennedy International Airport in New York.
ref: Tell me the shortest route to John F. Kennedy International Airport in New York.

src: 챗 지피티 포오와 챗 지피티 오원의 차이점은 어떻게 돼?
mt: What's the difference between Chat Zipiti Poo and Chat Gypty Owon?
ref: What is the difference between Chat GPT PoE and Chat GPT One?

src: 구글 미트라는 화상 채팅 어플에서 소리를 뮤트시키려면 어떻게 해야 돼?
mt: What should I do to mute sound from a video chat application called Google Mitt?
ref: How do I mute the sound in Google Meet, a video chat app?

src: 그 회사는 정말 프로의식이 없어. 전부 다 아마추어만도 못한 사람들이야.
mt: That company doesn't have a sense of professionalism. All of them are not even amateur.
ref: That company has absolutely no sense of professionalism. They're all amateurs.

src: 다음 주에 미팅이 있는데 내가 지금 미팅 디벨롭을 하려면 어떻게 해야 좋을까?
mt: I have a meeting next week, so what should I do if I want to get a meeting developer now?
ref: I have a meeting next week, how do I go about developing the meeting now?

src: 챗지피티의 문제점이 할루시네이션이라는데 그게 무슨 뜻인지 알아?
mt: The problem with Chatzipiti is that it's Halusination, do you know what that means?
ref: The problem with ChatGP is called hallucination. Do you know what that means?

src: 초보자부터 숙련자까지 모두 즐길 수 있는 다양한 산행 코스가 있어요.
mt: There are various hiking courses that you can enjoy from beginners to skilled people.
ref: There are various hiking trails that can be enjoyed by everyone from beginners to experienced hikers.

src: 엠지란 말은 도대체 어디서 온 말이야? 어떤 말의 줄임말인 거야?
mt: Where on earth does the word M.G come from? What does it mean?
ref: Where on earth does the word MG come from? What is it an abbreviation for?

src: 새로 산 백팩은 포켓이 많아서 여행 갈 때 정말 유용한 것 같아.
mt: I think the new backpack I bought is very useful when traveling because there are a lot of pocketets.
ref: The new backpack I bought has so many pockets — it's really useful for traveling.

src: 너 이번에 베트남 여행했다며. 베트남 사파에서 하이킹도 해봤어?
mt: You said you traveled to Vietnam this time. Have you also hiking in Sapa, Vietnam?
ref: You said you traveled to Vietnam this time. Did you go hiking in Sapa, Vietnam?

src: 일본에서 료칸 여행 좀 하려고 하는데 괜찮은 료칸 좀 추천해주라.
mt: I'm planning to travel to Ryokan in Japan, so please recommend me a good Ryokan.
ref: I'm planning a ryokan trip in Japan. Can you recommend some good ones?

src: 슬랙에서 사용할 신문 기사를 스크랩하고 싶어. 하나만 추천해 줄 수 있을까?
mt: I want to scrap a newspaper article to use in Slack. Can you recommend me one?
ref: I'd like to scrape newspaper articles to use in Slack. Can you recommend one?

src: 브루노마스랑 로제랑 같이 부른 아파트 동영상 조회수 몇이야?
mt: What is the number of views on the apartment video you sang with Brunomas and Rosé?
ref: How many views did the video of "Apartment" with Bruno Mars and Rosé get?

src: 대만은 여행 다녀오면 기념품으로 펑리수 밖에 사 올 게 없나?
mt: Do you have anything else to buy in Taiwan as a souvenir after a trip?
ref: When you travel to Taiwan, is there nothing you can buy as a souvenir other than fengli cakes?

src: 말레이시아 여행 때 먹었던 사테라는 꼬치구이가 가장 기억에 많이 남는다.
mt: The most memorable thing for me was the skewers, which I ate during my trip to Malaysia.
ref: The satay skewer I ate the most during my trip to Malaysia is what I remember the most.

src: 너는 투잡에 대해서 어떻게 생각해? 유명한 엔잡러에 대해서 소개해줘.
mt: What do you think about two jobs? Please introduce me to the famous entrants.
ref: What do you think about part-time jobs? Tell me about some famous part-time jobbers.

src: 야, 그거 알아? 청두 여행을 가면 판다를 꼭 보고 와야 된대.
mt: Hey, do you know that? You have to see Panda when you go on a trip to Chengdu.
ref: Hey, you know what? If you go to Chengdu, you absolutely have to see the pandas.

src: 일러스트와 그래픽아트라는 걸 수업시간에 배웠는데 두 개념의 차이가 뭔지 궁금해.
mt: I learned illustration and graphic art in class, and I wonder what the difference between the two concepts is.
ref: I learned about illustration and graphic art in class, but I'm curious about the difference between the two concepts.

src: 엔비디아 주가가 십년 뒤에는 얼마나 더 올라 있을까? 투자해도 괜찮을까?
mt: How much more Nvidia's stock price will rise in 10 years? Is it okay to invest?
ref: How much higher will Nvidia's stock price be in ten years? Is it worth investing in?

src: 산행 경험이 많이 없으시다면 비교적 쉬운 코스로 시작하시는 것이 좋죠.
mt: If you don't have much experience in hiking, it's better to start with a relatively easy course.
ref: If you don't have much hiking experience, it's a good idea to start with a relatively easy course.

src: 중국 여행 갔다가 동전이 남아 버렸네. 이게 다 몇 위안인겨?
mt: There are coins left while traveling to China. How many yuan is this?
ref: I came back from a trip to China and ended up with a bunch of coins. How many yuan is this altogether?

src: 이번에 일본 여행 갈 거거든? 숙소로는 일본 전통 료칸이 좋겠어.
mt: Are you going on a trip to Japan this time? Japanese traditional Ryokan would be good for accommodation.
ref: I’m planning a trip to Japan, and I’d really like to stay in a traditional ryokan.

src: 그럼 우리 이 나라 수도인 하노이 또 여행해볼까? 재밌을 것 같아.
mt: Shall we travel to Hanoi, the capital of this country? I think it'll be fun.
ref: Then, should we travel to Hanoi, the capital of our country, again? It seems like it would be fun.

src: 중국 관광지 중에 와이탄이 손꼽힐 정도이면 한 번쯤 가봐야 되지 않을까?
mt: Wouldn't it be better to visit at least once if Witan is one of the most popular tourist destinations in China?
ref: If the Bund is considered one of the top tourist destinations in China, shouldn't you visit it at least once?

src: 요즘 연말이라고 블랙프라이데이 세일하네. 나도 패딩 하나 새로 살까?
mt: Black Friday is on sale at the end of the year. Should I also buy a new padding?
ref: These days, there's a Black Friday sale because it's the end of the year. Should I buy a new padding?

src: 이젤의 주요 종류로는 표준 이젤과 드로잉 이젤이 있어요.
mt: The main types of bezel are standard bezel and drawing bezel.
ref: The main types of easels are standard easels and drawing easels.

src: 시카고에 있는 호텔 중에 일박에 백불 넘지 않은 곳들로만 좀 알려줘.
mt: Please let me know the hotels in Chicago that don't exceed $100 a day.
ref: Tell me about hotels in Chicago that cost less than $100 a night.

src: 내 엠비티아이는 아이에스티피인데 이 엠비티아이의 특징을 알려줘.
mt: My emblemia is Iestape, so please let me know the characteristics of this emblemia.
ref: My MBTI is an IST. Please tell me the characteristics of this MBTI.

src: 미국 대통령 링컨의 게티즈버그 연설 내용을 다섯 문장으로 요약해줘.
mt: Please summarize the contents of Lincoln's Gettyberg speech in five sentences.
ref: Summarize U.S. President Lincoln's Gettysburg Address in five sentences.

src: 사파에 가면 카약 투어가 유명하대. 한번 꼭 해보는 거 어때?
mt: The kayak tour is famous in Sapa. Why don't you try it?
ref: Kayaking tours are said to be popular in Sapa. How about trying it at least once?

src: 걔는 내 친구긴 하지만 너무 투머치 토커야. 그렇지 않아?
mt: He's my friend, but he's too much a Tumutch Toker, isn't he?
ref: He's my friend, but he's a bit too talkative, isn't he?

src: 너 요즘 엠지 용어 좀 알아? 줄임말이나 티엠아이 이런 거?
mt: Do you know the term M.G these days? What do you mean in short or T.M?
ref: Do you know any MG terminology these days? Abbreviations, TMI, things like that?

src: 퍼플렉시티라는 에이아이가 나온 걸로 알고 있는데 이걸 검색 엔진에 활용할 수 있을까?
mt: As far as I know, a child named Purple City came out, can I use it for a search engine?
ref: I know there's an AI called Perplexity, can this be used in a search engine?

src: 베트남 여행했는데 베트남에는 까이랑 수상시장이 있거든. 되게 독특하게 생겼더라.
mt: I traveled to Vietnam, but Vietnam has a water market with black hair. It looks very unique.
ref: I traveled to Vietnam, and there's this floating market called Cai Rang. It looked really unique.

src: 겨울에 후쿠오카로 여행을 갈 예정인데 나베로 유명한 식당 찾아봐 줘.
mt: I'm going on a trip to Fukuoka in winter, so please look for a famous restaurant in Nabe.
ref: I'm planning a trip to Fukuoka in the winter, so please find a restaurant famous for nabe.

src: 이번 회의는 웨비나로 할 건데 그러면 스크린샷을 좀 전송해 줘야 하지 않을까?
mt: We're going to have this meeting as a webina, so shouldn't we send you a screen shot?
ref: We're doing this meeting as a webinar — maybe we should send over some screenshots?

src: 이번 휴가 때 타이베이로 여행 갈 건데 갈만한 야시장 추천 좀 해줄래?
mt: I'm going on a trip to Taipei this vacation, could you recommend me a night market for me?
ref: I'm going on a trip to Taipei for my vacation. Could you recommend any good night markets to visit?

src: 너 일본 삿포로에 살지? 내가 여행 갈 건데 가이드 좀 부탁해도 될까?
mt: Do you live in Sapporo, Japan? I'm going on a trip, can I ask for a guide?
ref: Do you live in Sapporo, Japan? I'm planning a trip there, could you please be my guide?

src: 요즘 유행하는 밈을 가르쳐줄래? 너무 뒤떨어지고 있는 것 같아서 그래.
mt: Can you teach me the memes that are popular these days? I think they're falling behind.
ref: Can you teach me some of the trending memes these days? I feel like I'm falling behind so much.

src: 피엔지는 그 사진 파일 그거고 피이지는 뭐야? 처음 들어봤어.
mt: That's the photo file of P&G and what's P/G? It's my first time listening to it.
ref: PNG is that photo file, and what is PEG? This is the first time I've heard of it.

src: 유럽의 어떤 나라에서 오로라가 관측되는지 알려줄 수 있어? 겨울에 여행하고 싶거든.
mt: Can you tell me which countries in Europe are observing aurora? I want to travel in winter.
ref: Can you tell me which countries in Europe I can see the Northern Lights in? I want to travel there in the winter.

src: 코로나가 한창 심했을 때는 자가격리 때문에 해외여행 나가기가 많이 힘들었었지.
mt: When COVID-19 was in full swing, it was hard to go on an overseas trip because of the self-price.
ref: When COVID-19 was at its peak, it was hard to travel abroad because of quarantine requirements.

src: 에이아이 챗봇아, 어메니티로 샴푸 조말론 거 나오는 호텔 알려줘.
mt: A-i Chatbot, please let me know the hotel where the shampoo Jonathan comes out with an amenities.
ref: AI Chatbot, please let me know which hotels provide Jo Malone shampoo as part of their amenities.

src: 인스파이어 리조트랑 파라다이스 시티 중 호캉스로 더 좋은 곳은 어디야?
mt: Which is better, Inspire Resort or Paradise City?
ref: Which is better for a vacation, Inspire Resort or Paradise City?

src: 엠비티아이 아이에스티피랑 이엔에프피의 특성과 그 궁합 좀 알려줘.
mt: Please let me know the characteristics and compatibility of MBI IST and E&F.
ref: Please tell me the characteristics and compatibility of MBTI IST and ENF.
